### Button
  A versatile button component with primary, secondary, and ghost variants,
multiple sizes, loading state, and disabled state.
  Import: `import { Button } from 'test-client-design-system'`
  Props:
    - variant: 'primary' | 'secondary' | 'ghost' (optional) — The variant of the button
    - size: 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg' (optional) — The size of the button
    - loading: boolean (optional) — If true, the button will show a loading spinner
    - className: string (optional) — Additional class names to apply to the button

